import React from "react";
import { Box, Flex, Spacer, VStack, Image, HStack, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import footerLogo from "../images/Asset 20@4x.png"

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <Box backgroundColor="#D9D9D9">
            <footer>
                <Flex
                    margin={"0 188px"}
                    color="white"
                    justifyContent="center"
                    alignItems="center"
                    height={"256px"}
                >
                    <Box p='4'>
                        <Image src={footerLogo} width={"124px"} height={"auto"}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Spacer />
                    <Box p='4' bg='green.400'>
                        <HStack>
                            <Text>

                            </Text>
                        </HStack>
                    </Box>
                    <Spacer />
                    <Box p='4' bg='red.400'>
                        Box 1
                    </Box>
                    <Spacer />
                    <Box p='4' bg='green.400'>
                        Box 2
                    </Box>
                </Flex>
            </footer>
        </Box>
    );
};
export default Footer;
